{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"Console.log()","mdn_url":"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/log","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console_API\">Console API</a></strong></li><li><strong><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>Console</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Métodos</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/assert\"><code>assert()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/clear\"><code>clear()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/count\"><code>count()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/countReset\"><code>countReset()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/debug\"><code>debug()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/dir\"><code>dir()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/dirxml\"><code>dirxml()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/error\"><code>error()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/group\"><code>group()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupCollapsed\"><code>groupCollapsed()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/groupEnd\"><code>groupEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/info\"><code>info()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/log\"><code>log()</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profile\"><code>profile()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/profileEnd\"><code>profileEnd()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/table\"><code>table()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/time\"><code>time()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/timeEnd\"><code>timeEnd()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/timeLog\"><code>timeLog()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-nonstandard\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-nonstandard\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/timeStamp\"><code>timeStamp()</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console/trace\"><code>trace()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console/warn\"><code>warn()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Páginas relacionadas a Console API</summary><ol><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/Window/console\"><code>Window.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/WorkerGlobalScope/console\"><code>WorkerGlobalScope.console</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"><div class=\"notecard warning\" id=\"sect2\"><p><strong>Non-standard:</strong> This feature is non-standard and is not on a standards track. Do not use it on production sites facing the Web: it will not work for every user. There may also be large incompatibilities between implementations and the behavior may change in the future.</p></div></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"summary","title":"Sumário","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Exibe uma mensagem na console do navegador.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"syntax","title":"Syntax","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"syntaxbox notranslate\">console.log(<em>obj1</em>[, <em>obj2</em>, ..., <em>objN]</em>);\nconsole.log(<em>msg</em>[, <em>subst1</em>, ..., <em>substN]</em>);\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"parameters","title":"Parameters","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"obj1\"><code>obj1</code> ... <code>objN</code></dt>\n <dd>Uma lista de objetos&nbsp;JavaScript para exibir. A representação por escrito de cada um desses objetos é exibida na ordem com a qual foram inseridos na função.</dd>\n <dt id=\"msg\"><code>msg</code></dt>\n <dd>Uma string JavaScript com zero ou mais substituições.</dd>\n <dt id=\"subst1\"><code>subst1</code> ... <code>substN</code></dt>\n <dd>Strings ou objetos JavaScript para substituirem as marcações de substituição em&nbsp;<code>msg</code>. Estas substituições ocorrem de um para um e&nbsp;na ordem em que são passadas para a console.log.</dd>\n</dl>\n\n<p>Veja&nbsp;<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/console#outputting_text_to_the_console\" title=\"DOM/console#Outputting_text_to_the_console\">Exibindo texto na console</a> na documentação do objeto <a href=\"/pt-BR/docs/Web/API/Console\"><code>console</code></a> para mais detalhes.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specification","title":"Especificação","isH3":false,"content":"<p>Não faz parte de nenhuma especificação.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"browser_compatibility","title":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><div class=\"notecard note\" id=\"sect3\"><strong><a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/browser-compat-data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Estamos convertendo nossos dados de compatibilidade para o formato JSON</a></strong>.\n            Esta tabela de compatibilidade ainda usa o formato antigo,\n            pois ainda não convertemos os dados que ela contém.\n            <strong><a href=\"/en-US/docs/MDN/Structures/Compatibility_tables\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">Descubra como você pode ajudar! (en-US)</a></strong></div>\n\n<div class=\"htab\" id=\"sect4\">\n    <a id=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\" name=\"AutoCompatibilityTable\"></a>\n    <ul>\n        <li class=\"selected\"><a href=\"#compat-desktop\">Desktop</a></li>\n        <li><a href=\"#compat-mobile\">Dispositivo móvel</a></li>\n    </ul>\n</div><p></p>\n\n<div id=\"compat-desktop\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Chrome</th>\n   <th>Firefox (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>Internet Explorer</th>\n   <th>Opera</th>\n   <th>Safari</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/4\" title=\"Released on 2011-03-22.\">4.0</a> (2.0)</td>\n   <td>8</td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Strings de substituição</td>\n   <td>\n    <p><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></p>\n\n    <p>28</p>\n\n    <p>%d - se um valor fracional negativo é passado, ele será arredondado para baixo, exemplo: -0,35 será arredondado para 1</p>\n   </td>\n   <td><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Mozilla/Firefox/Releases/9\" title=\"Released on 2011-12-20.\">9.0</a> (9.0)</td>\n   <td>\n    <p>10 - parcial</p>\n\n    <p>%c - não suportado<br>\n     <span style=\"line-height: 1.572;\">%d - irá renderizar como 0 quando NaN</span></p>\n   </td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n   <td><span style=\"color: #888\" title=\"Please update this with the earliest version of support.\">(Yes)</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<div id=\"compat-mobile\">\n<table class=\"compat-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th>Característica</th>\n   <th>Android</th>\n   <th>Firefox Mobile (Gecko)</th>\n   <th>IE Mobile</th>\n   <th>Opera Mobile</th>\n   <th>Safari Mobile</th>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Suporte básico</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>4.0 (2.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td>Strings de substituição</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td>9.0 (9.0)</td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n   <td><span title=\"Compatibility unknown; please update this.\" style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 0);\">?</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>\n</div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_também","title":"Ver também","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.opera.com/dragonfly/documentation/console/\" rel=\" noopener\">Opera Dragonfly documentation: Console</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/gg589530\" rel=\" noopener\">MSDN: Using the F12 Tools Console to View Errors and Status</a></li>\n <li><a href=\"https://getfirebug.com/wiki/index.php/Console_API\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Firebug wiki: Console API</a> - Firebug supports additional features in its console.log() implementation, such as <a href=\"http://www.softwareishard.com/blog/firebug/firebug-tip-styled-logging/\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">styled logging</a>.</li>\n <li><a href=\"https://nodejs.org/docs/latest/api/console.html#console_console_log_data\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">NodeJS: Console API</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Sumário","id":"summary"},{"text":"Syntax","id":"syntax"},{"text":"Parameters","id":"parameters"},{"text":"Especificação","id":"specification"},{"text":"Compatibilidade com navegadores","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"Ver também","id":"ver_também"}],"summary":"Exibe uma mensagem na console do navegador.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch"},{"title":"console.log()","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"console.log()","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"console.log()","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"console.log()","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"pl","native":"Polski"},{"title":"Console.log()","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title